			"displayName": "SQL查询",
			"description": "要执行的SQL查询，有关传统SQL语法的更多信息请<a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/bigquery/docs/reference/standard-sql/query-syntax\" target=\"_blank\">点击此处</a>",
